How to install Textmate plugin for an AADL support ?
----------------------------------------------------

Copy AADL.tmbundle directory into your $HOME/Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles/.
The following command will do that :
mkdir -p $HOME/Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles/ && cp -r AADL.tmbundle
$HOME/Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles/

If you have an access to ocarina's repository, you can also use 
the installation script located in this directory.
